==============
How to install
==============

1. Unpack
$ tar -zxvf slim-debian-simple.tar.gz


2. Copy extracted folder to Slim theme directory
# cp -R slim-debian-simple/ /usr/share/slim/themes


3. Open Slim config file
# nano /etc/slim.conf


4. Locate and change the following line
current_theme		slim-debian-simple


I hope you enjoy!





